'''Ubisoft Shanghai''' is a [[China|Chinese]] [[video game developer]] whose headquarters is located in [[Shanghai]]. The studio is known for working in various games in the ''[[Tom Clancy]]'' franchise. The studio is also the second largest Chinese video game studio and the second largest [[Ubisoft]] studio.
